# hooks/

Stores Claude Code hook configurations that automate workflow validation and compliance checks. Hooks are triggered on specific events (PostToolUse, etc.) and enforce project conventions — in this case, the Highlander Rule by validating that newly created files are registered in the Intent module registry.

## Files

- `module_check_hook.json` -- PostToolUse hook that validates new files against intent/llm/MODULES.md registration
